# YT Agent — Colab Secrets
#
# Add ONLY these in Colab's 🔑 Secrets panel. Everything else (NIM key,
# Shutterstock token, Pexels/Pixabay/Coverr keys, etc.) is managed in the
# dashboard's "API Keys" page and pulled from Hostinger on startup.

# ── REQUIRED (bootstrap) ──────────────────────────────────────
FTP_HOST                  ftp.yourdomain.com
FTP_USER                  u123456789
FTP_PASS                  <your hostinger FTP password>
PUBLIC_BASE_URL           https://yourdomain.com/yt-agent

# ── Optional ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
FTP_BASE_DIR              /public_html/yt-agent
FTP_PORT                  21
FTP_USE_TLS               1                  # 0 = plain FTP
INSTANCE_LABEL            colab-gpu          # appears in the dashboard
